    "body": "I think this issue is more related to the engine than the helper. Do you want the same behaviour as Tim described? ie Bounding box filtering and aroundLatLng ordering?\r\n\r\nAn option which is possible, but only when the result set is small enough, is to do a query for all the items in the bounding box, and manually sorting them based on the geo location.",
